item.title: Powell suggested tech giants fueling the AI boom and GDP hardly care about Fed rate tweaks. They just proved him right
item.description: While Wall Street seems to live and die on the slightest hints about the Federal Reserve’s rate stance, Chair Jerome Powell doesn’t think the tech giants behind the AI boom will be swayed by incremental moves in monetary policy.
